reviews.review_text: Good Times and met Mickey Out on Spring tour with a few other deadicated SIU - Carbondale students. We scored tickets the day of the show at the box office first thing in the morning. Walked by Mickey Hart later in the day and everyone in our crew was afraid to speak to him except me. I said hello and all he did was give me a giant bear hug then left - it was awesome. Remember it being a cold and snowy day. Also remember the China rider being wonderful and this recording backs that up. thank you Charlie really good stuff.
